## Key Fixes in This Version

| Fix | What changed |
|-----|-------------|
| **`emitLS` PC-relative** | `rn==15` now allowed when `immO&&pre&&!wb` — folds address statically |
| **`setV_add/sub` shift** | `rlwinm TE,TE,29,28,28` (right shift 3) instead of wrong `rlwinm TE,TE,3,3,3` |
| **`sLsrI/sAsrI` carry** | Carry bit is at `bit(i-1)`, extracted with `rlwinm TC,s,(33-i)&31,31,31` |
| **`sRorI` carry** | Same `(33-i)&31` formula |
| **`setC_imm`** | Renamed from `setC_bit0`; uses `rlwinm TA,cr,29,29,29` to move bit0→bit29 |
| **`primeCarry`** | Uses `addic r0,TA,-1` (correct EABI: result goes to r0, not a used reg) |
| **`emitBX_target`** | Single canonical function; old broken `emitBX_SCR0` removed |
| **No `DebugLog` in hot path** | Logging only during compile (once per unique PC), not every execution |
| **`emitBlockXfer` pcForR15** | Changed from `curPC+12` to `curPC+8` (ARM STM stores PC+8) |



